REAL-TIME ENGAGEMENT SOLUTION

   Greetings and thanks for stopping by.

   Regrettably, CoveritLive ceased its service offering effective 31
   December 2018. If you’re an existing CoveritLive customer and didn’t
   get the email notifications, you can request a copy by emailing
   ITsupport@scribblelive.com.

   If you are here because you need a proven solution to report breaking
   news, publish real-time updates, or to engage with fans through social
   media and live Q&A’s, then check out the live publishing and social
   engagement product called Engage, by ScribbleLive. It has all the
   features of CoveritLive and offers a much more robust and feature-rich
   mobile experience.

   We’re here to help and answer any questions you might have, feel free
   to contact us if you have any additional questions.

   Sincerely,

   The ScribbleLive team

   Get the CiL Newsletter:
