    1. DEFINITIONS
       “Account” means the system on our Site by which you register and
       thereafter authenticate your privileges to access our Service.
       “User Engagement Minutes (UEM)” is an estimate of the aggregate
       number of minutes users have viewed your content.
       “Company” means Scribble Technologies, Inc., a corporation formed
       under the laws of the Province of Ontario, Canada; “us” and “we”
       are both synonymous with Company, and references to “our” is
